文化小站 / Culture 101

🌕 中秋节 • Mid‑Autumn Festival

农历八月十五，赏月团圆、吃月饼、提灯笼。传说有嫦娥、玉兔、吴刚。圆月象征团圆与思念。

On the 15th day of the 8th lunar month, families reunite to admire the full moon, share mooncakes and lanterns—symbols of togetherness and longing.

📜 水调歌头《明月几时有》

苏轼 1076 年名篇，借月寄怀，表达“人有悲欢离合，月有阴晴圆缺”的人生感悟，结句“但愿人长久，千里共婵娟”。

Su Shi’s 1076 classic reflects on reunion and separation through the moon; closing wish: “May we all be blessed with longevity, though thousands of miles apart.”

🦁 舞狮 • Lion Dance

寓意驱邪纳福、开运迎吉。分南北狮，锣鼓点配合腾挪跳跃；常见于新春、开业、庆典。

A symbol of luck and protection; Southern/Northern styles with acrobatics to drum–gong rhythms.

🎭 京剧 • Peking Opera

“唱念做打”兼具，生旦净丑四行当；脸谱色彩寓意性格，如红忠勇、黑刚直、白多疑。

Blends singing, speech, movement, combat; role types (sheng, dan, jing, chou) with symbolic face‑paint colors.

🎼 古筝 • Guzheng

21弦拨弹乐器，常用五声音阶，滑音与摇指展现流水般音色。

A 21‑string plucked zither known for glissandos and shimmering tremolos.

🎼 阮 • Ruan

圆形共鸣箱、四弦拨弹，音色浑厚明亮，常见于民乐合奏与戏曲伴奏。

A round‑bodied lute with a mellow, bright tone used in ensembles and opera.

🎻 京胡 • Jinghu

二弦拉弦乐器，是京剧主奏，音色尖亮、穿透力强，常与唱腔呼应。

A two‑string spike fiddle leading Peking Opera with a brilliant, penetrating sound.

互动游园 / Hands‑on Activities

$1/张活动票；每个活动需 1–10 张不等，可在现场购票台购买。

🎯 套圈 · Ring Toss

用小圈套住奖品，套中就赢！

Ring Toss – Toss rings to land on prizes and win!

🏺 投壶 · Pitch Pot

投箭进壶，命中拿奖品！

Pitch Pot – Throw arrows into a pot to win prizes!

🥢 筷子比赛 · Chopstick Challenge

30秒夹糖果，比谁多谁赢

Chopstick Challenge – Players pick candies in 30 seconds; the winner wins prizes!

🎨 漆扇 · Painted Fan

DIY彩绘或装饰纸扇，做专属小扇子

Painted Fan – Decorate a paper fan with colors and patterns.

🏮 中国手工 · Chinese Handicrafts

制作灯笼、拉拉龙或漆扇

Chinese Handicrafts – Make lanterns, pull dragons, or painted fans.

🥮 手工月饼 · Handmade Mooncakes

亲手制作迷你月饼，玩儿得开心

Handmade Mooncakes – Make your own mini mooncakes.

🍡 手工冰糖葫芦 · Handmade Candied Hawthorn Skewers

亲手裹糖浆，做甜甜的冰糖葫芦串串

Handmade Candied Hawthorn Skewers – Make your own candied fruit skewers by dipping fruit in sugar syrup.

💅 中式美甲 · Nail Art

中式国潮彩绘指甲，美美哒

Nail Art – Get fun nail designs painted on your nails.

✨ 彩绘纹身 · Hannah Tattoo

贴或画临时纹身，闪亮手臂

Hannah Tattoo – Apply temporary tattoos on your skin.

👘 传统服装发饰 · Traditional Costume &Accessories

试穿中国传统服装，拍美照

Traditional Costume &Accessories – Try on traditional Chinese clothes and take photos.

🍿 爆米花 · Popcorn

现场领取热腾腾爆米花

Popcorn – Enjoy freshly made popcorn.

🍧 刨冰 · Snow Ice

消暑刨冰或冰沙，清凉一夏

Snow Ice – Enjoy a refreshing shaved ice treat.
